      <title>为什么手写比打字更有利于思考和学习</title>
      <link>https://www.npr.org/sections/health-shots/2024/05/11/1250529661/handwriting-cursive-typing-schools-learning-brain</link>
      <description><![CDATA[研究人员发现，手写对大脑的影响是打字所无法比拟的，这引发了人们对放弃这种古老做法的代价的质疑，尤其是对孩子来说。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.npr.org/sections/health-shots/2024/05/11/1250529661/handwriting-cursive-typing-schools-learning-brain</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 11 May 2024 11:00:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
